451 A.2d 562 Equibank, etc. v. Gilman, et ux. Appeal of Robert Woods. Argued February 8, 1982. Stephen Israel, for appellant; Sidney R. Finkel, did not file a brief on behalf of Equibank, appellee; Alfred C. Maiello, did not file a brief on behalf of Douglas *624Gilman, appellee; James David Elder, did not file a brief on behalf of Lucille Gilman, appellee; Norman Paul Wolken, did not file a brief on behalf of Sheriff, participating party.

Reargument Denied Oct. 28, 1982.

Petition for Allowance of Appeal Denied Dec. 6, 1982.
